{"tid":1074120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳方安生訪美　獲彭斯接見談一國兩制","createTime":"2019-03-23T07:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T05:51:38.000Z","uid":141151,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9f8edbe788af79524f53397b31d478f2431b1fc9","tid":1074120,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:21:16.000Z","msg":"陳方安生訪美　獲彭斯接見談一國兩制 (09:22)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190323/s00001/1553302728715/%e9%99%b3%e6%96%b9%e5%ae%89%e7%94%9f%e8%a8%aa%e7%be%8e-%e7%8d%b2%e5%bd%ad%e6%96%af%e6%8e%a5%e8%a6%8b%e8%ab%87%e4%b8%80%e5%9c%8b%e5%85%a9%e5%88%b6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190323%2Fs00001%2F1553302728715%2F%25e9%2599%25b3%25e6%2596%25b9%25e5%25ae%2589%25e7%2594%259f%25e8%25a8%25aa%25e7%25be%258e-%25e7%258d%25b2%25e5%25bd%25ad%25e6%2596%25af%25e6%258e%25a5%25e8%25a6%258b%25e8%25ab%2587%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%2588%25b6&d=INFrb%2BpCZNVkt1J9J2ljEAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=ced3d322\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190323%2Fs00001%2F1553302728715%2F%25e9%2599%25b3%25e6%2596%25b9%25e5%25ae%2589%25e7%2594%259f%25e8%25a8%25aa%25e7%25be%258e-%25e7%258d%25b2%25e5%25bd%25ad%25e6%2596%25af%25e6%258e%25a5%25e8%25a6%258b%25e8%25ab%2587%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%2588%25b6&h=2f04ea6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190323/s00001/1553302728715/%e9%99%b3%e6%96%b9%e5%ae%89%e7%94%9f%e8%a8%aa%e7%be%8e-%e7%8d%b2%e5%bd%ad%e6%96%af%e6%8e%a5%e8%a6%8b%e8%ab%87%e4%b8%80%e5%9c%8b%e5%85%a9%e5%88%b6</a><br />\n<br />\n前政務司長陳方安生、民主派立法會議員郭榮鏗及莫乃光獲邀訪問美國，其中陳方安生獲高規格接待，在華盛頓獲美國副總統彭斯（Mike Pence）接見；三人亦與美國國家安全委員會成員會面。<br />\n<br />\n陳方安生與彭斯短暫交談，談論香港情況，尤其是「一國兩制」保障的人權和自由的實踐。<br />\n<br />\n陳方安生、郭榮鏗與莫乃光又與美國國家安全委員會亞太資深主任Matt Pottinger等官員會面。美國國務院發表了《美國&mdash;香港政策法》年度報告，三人向國家安全委員會重申，支持「一國兩制」，這不單是符合香港利益，更對中美關係甚為重要。<br />\n<br />\n會上亦談及多項議題，包括特區政府最新的移交逃犯建議、驅趕外國記者、民主發展，以及DQ事件等。雙方均同意政策法是否延續，與「一國兩制」運作是否良好有密切關連，以及香港必須保障自由、民主、法治等基礎要素。<br />\n<br />\n陳方安生將於當地時間下周一（25日），於傳統基金會發表演說。三人其後將拜會美國眾議院議長佩洛西（Nancy Pelosi）。"},{"pid":"cc24c612f48fdbe03d35d670aecacb799a5438ee","tid":1074120,"uid":213877,"like":4,"dislike":26,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:55:45.000Z","msg":"侵侵都係門口狗黎<br />\n<br />\n係要搞香港係要搞支那洗等到今時今日？咪又係為錢"},{"pid":"4d228e4bb24b5e51cdb779878c0a306079a730bf","tid":1074120,"uid":213877,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T07:56:10.000Z","msg":"商家佬最後都係為利益"},{"pid":"cd7b42b668ff8756c50afc838e8dd06cf7bed713","tid":1074120,"uid":238370,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:12:56.000Z","msg":"民主阿婆果然有頭有面，副總統都見到面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3091751e5eb291cbe8650a4d7db9058890536953","tid":1074120,"uid":7369,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:14:33.000Z","msg":"其實都係門面嘢，叫做畀少少壓力習總"},{"pid":"22c8e8be377b935ae202e6542a0d81167ef6b2ab","tid":1074120,"uid":52869,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:17:08.000Z","msg":"門面嘢都好, 777有冇呢個機會?"},{"pid":"52bc1aa9b65211a4bb92f446cdcaa05a475e36d5","tid":1074120,"uid":7369,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"22c8e8be377b935ae202e6542a0d81167ef6b2ab","tid":1074120,"uid":52869,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:17:08.000Z","msg":"門面嘢都好, 777有冇呢個機會?"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:20:13.000Z","msg":"林鄭咪見咗韓國瑜囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277ab994c53faa6cf90ff7b072dd4e91e0fe0552","tid":1074120,"uid":51937,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"52bc1aa9b65211a4bb92f446cdcaa05a475e36d5","tid":1074120,"uid":7369,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"